{"tid":1531010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［冷靜］對家不停放假料，就係想有真料爆出嚟時都煲唔大","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:36:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9b65006700c6dfe7b3279cbb3612c9b239ad5d","tid":1531010,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"哩一兩星期明顯多咗好多不利政府既流料爆出嚟<br />\n事後證明係假<br />\n累好多人包括外媒、kol炒車<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者整體既公信力係受損<br />\n<br />\n再係咁，日後有真料流出嚟<br />\n甚至有人證出嚟講野<br />\n外媒等都會唔敢落注煲大件事<br />\n我相信哩個係政府啲所謂心戰室既策略<br />\n<br />\n希望各位任何爆料都盡可能fact checked<br />\n未證實時就算share都要指明係&lsquo;傳&rsquo;、&lsquo;未證實&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住鳩噏冇所謂<br />\n總之唱衰政府就得<br />\n<br />\n政府既宣傳渠道多抗爭者n倍<br />\n但正因為佢哋冇人信，抗爭者大致相當可信<br />\n所以抗爭者輿論先贏"},{"pid":"4793bfcc411af3b4752459eefb9158e492922366","tid":1531010,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"諗同"},{"pid":"65b64e103315d493ee1dbfb835fb6df67577b6be","tid":1531010,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7543b9e1b73c547f02ffca0936d628bf9b0dd33c","tid":1531010,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"冇錯冇錯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行動為主 評論為輔</strong></span>"},{"pid":"29a0505fdfee4fcead7a9553f5deb574ac97310d","tid":1531010,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:10:34.000Z","msg":"推 明顯似有人死左 大家要等消息"},{"pid":"4313abd02399c6fc663ff2211b0146bbbd28ae6e","tid":1531010,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82101288e697c193a66d3bfbfc6787a4001965d7","tid":1531010,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl